quant_functionality
------------------

l1: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z (F w (g y z) Ôćö h w y = h w z) $ by all_elim [#1]
l2: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ z (F w (g x z) Ôćö h w x = h w z) $ by all_elim [l1]
l3: $ _ ÔŐó F w (g x y) Ôćö h w x = h w y $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ _ ÔŐó F w (g x z) Ôćö h w x = h w z $ by all_elim [l2]
l5: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ z (F w (g y z) Ôćö h w y = h w z) $ by all_elim [l1]
l6: $ _ ÔŐó F w (g y z) Ôćö h w y = h w z $ by all_elim [l5]
l7: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) $ by ax []
l8: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó F w (g x y) $ by and_elim_l [l7]
l9: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó F w (g x z) $ by and_elim_r [l7]
l10: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó h w x = h w y $ by iff_elim_l [l3, l8]
l11: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó h w x = h w z $ by iff_elim_l [l4, l9]
l12: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó h w y = h w x $ by eq_symm [l10]
l13: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó h w y = h w z $ by eq_transitivity [l12, l11]
l14: $ (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) ÔŐó F w (g y z) $ by iff_elim_r [l6, l13]
l15: $ _ ÔŐó (F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) Ôćĺ F w (g y z) $ by imp_intro [l14]
l16: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ z ((F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) Ôćĺ F w (g y z)) $ by all_intro [l15]
l17: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z ((F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) Ôćĺ F w (g y z)) $ by all_intro [l16]
l18: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ x ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z ((F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) Ôćĺ F w (g y z)) $ by all_intro [l17]
l19: $ _ ÔŐó ÔłÇ w ÔłÇ x ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z ((F w (g x y) Ôłž F w (g x z)) Ôćĺ F w (g y z)) $ by all_intro [l18]

